---
title: Smart Lemony Pork Chops with Raisin-Studded Couscous
description: Indulge in a burst of citrusy delight with these lemony pork chops, with a crispy panko topping that adds crunch. Served over fluffy couscous studded with raisins, it's a symphony of flavours that'll have your taste buds singing for an encore!

